						<div class="postbody">Ha.  That's funny.  I didn't realize NOP was actually an instruction.  I just thought it was an abbreviation for a family of potential operations that acted as null.  This is where having studied computer science probably would've paid off!  haha<br /><br />And...whoa!  After counting cycles (and understanding how that works) and doing the math on the scroll...........<br /><br /><div class="attachtitle">Attachment:</div><div class="attachcontent">
